Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friendship. Romance. Mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we cherish them we can continue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Princess and Queen, the two mothers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key to everything lies with pops
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth, (
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A.childin appearance\Nwith the I.Q. of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left unsolved\Nwith Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pops is asked to find\Nthe person who is after the life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of Mr Mikio Fujieda for\Na fee of 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He thinks this is an easy case, and\Nholds a celebration party in advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,only to spend a lot of money.\NHe couldn't close the case, and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he is in debt of about 8 million yen.\NHe is shocked and takes to his bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acting on behalf of pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's mom goes to the client's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There. she happens "O-meet,™ mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, Mr. Mikio Fujieda is\Nkilled ih a closed room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,(1% $87)\NTwo Princesses of a Kind Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I Its Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! And Yukiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,@h, I'm here for...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'mihere on behalf of my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,\".ui \ .\NHe got a request for finding\Na person living on the premises
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that is after the life of Mr. Mikio Fujieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did he know that the person\NIS among the people on the premises?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These were placed under\Nthe pillow of Mr. Mikio Fujieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch behind you!,\NI'll send you to heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So was this used bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who could have done a thing like that\Nexcept someone living in thehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime took place at-about...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it about 8 o'clock pm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's when all of us were watching\Nthe display of the surveillance camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fujieda stood up\Nholding his hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was shot and fell down-to-the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We hurried to the room and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,heard two gun shots from inside the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We broke the door. went inside the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found the gun, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gun is a Colt Compact 45 automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were three cartridges-beside-the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the number of cartridges coincides\Nwith the number of bullet wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the culprit\Nshot across this window
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and hurried out of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we have to consider\Nthe possibility of a culprit from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This towel with a burn on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is probably
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is probably
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,burnt when the culprit wrapped the towel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,around the gun when firing.\NAnd tried to hide the powder traces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or tried to muffle the gun shot but failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. ladies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Chiba, you go find out\Nwhere and how the gun was obtained.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagiyyou go find out if any\NSUSPICIOUS person was around-or seen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wu. /\Nes\ I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check the bullets in the body against.\NThe bullet left under the pillow-please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:05:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Inspector. bring the lab people\Nand come with me to thé living-room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll check the gun powder traces\Non all the people in the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and start questioning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on Mrs. Kudo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take it easy with Eri. Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eri is trying her best
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For her. 10 million yen is at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!!\NMouri Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to, NEED TO.\NDon't do anything unnecessary\Nuntil I come back. Er."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, one by one let's have each\Nof you talk to the Inspector
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Mikio was shot in the audio room, ~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for about 3 minutes until\Nwe found the dead body,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where were you all, and\Nwhat were you all doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to my room to get the key
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and ran to the audio room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ON Iv\NIl called the police and an ambulance\Non the phone in my room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I stayed. in.my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you knew your husband was shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:06:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, there could be\Na man with a gun around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.39,0:06:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, you know I was\Nwatching Mikio get shot and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,go down on the display\Nwith the butler and the others!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you must suspect someone,\Nyou can pick on Shigeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cause he went out of the meénitering\Nroom just before Mikio went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to write the manuscript\NI was working on in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ZrBut I stopped writing and joined Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the others to go up to the audio room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the two gun shots\Nin front of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I couldn't have possibly done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did: you hear any suspicious\Nsound or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sound of the classical\Nmusic was so loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Inspector,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but do you mind if I sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can sit down, Mr. Ueki\Nand everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer to keep standing.\NIt's easier on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I caught a man loitering\Naround the garden, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come on up quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is Mr. Doi, the gardener.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gardener, is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been like this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't say anything.\NDoesn't answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Doi was at a place in the garden\Nvery far from the audio room,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for at least three minutes after\NMr Fujieda was shot at 8 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Doi was seen in the surveillance\Ncamera and on the display!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was absorbed in gardening\Neven after the incident
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and just didn't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing is believing. they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you care to go and take a look\Nat the video of the surveillance camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seems to be in the garden\Nwhen he was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he disappeared right after it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the light is seen on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light is flickering,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that means he is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if there were cameras in all of the rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we would be able to tell when,\Nwhere, and who did what
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:07:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But these pictures tell\Nyou enough, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce of an outsider\NIS breaking in is slight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the possibility that the crime was\Ncommitted by an insider is more likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are so many cameras around but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there is no picture of a suspicious\Nperson on any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime was committed by\Na person who knows precisel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where the cameras are located- see /
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we have four suspects to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When they commit the crime, 1t seems\Nthat two of them are always together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how about going after their motives?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you are very quiet today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You usually get all excited over a case.\NWhat' s come over you?
